<div class="table-deal">
  <div class="row container">
    <div class="col s12 m6 l3">
      <div class="center promo">
        <i class="material-icons cyan-text">dns</i>
        <p class="table-caption">Networks</p>
        <p class="light center">
          We manage the setup of your entire network - from running ethernet
          lines to configuring servers. We'll make sure that your network and devices
          are running at their full potential.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m6 l3">
      <div class="center promo promo-example">
        <i class="material-icons cyan-text">lock_outline</i>
        <p class="table-caption">Security</p>
        <p class="light center">
          We know your data is important, and specialize in keping it safe.
          Our team has years of experience with information security and will help
          you minimize risks to your network.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m6 l3">
      <div class="center promo promo-example">
        <i class="material-icons cyan-text">playlist_add_check</i>
        <p class="table-caption">Consulting</p>
        <p class="light center">
          Whether you're planning a new project, looking to upgrade your
          hardware, or simply want us to take a look at your network - we'll help
          you make sure it's done right.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m6 l3">
      <div class="center promo promo-example">
        <i class="material-icons cyan-text">build</i>
        <p class="table-caption">Support</p>
        <p class="light center">
          Each of our clients receive a login to our support system to ensure a
          timely response. Just file a ticket with us and we'll get back to you
          ASAP. Simple as that.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

